<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link><description>界面快报</description><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://res.jiemian.com/assets/wap/common/img/jm-new-logo.png</url><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 00:00:03 +0800</lastBuildDate><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 00:00:03 +0800</pubDate><item><title>2024中秋档预售票房破1000万</title><link>https://www.jiemian.com/article/11677182.html</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-content"><p>据猫眼专业版数据，截至9月4日23时14分，2024年中秋档预售总票房（含点映）破1000万元，《野孩子》领跑中秋档预售票房榜。</p>
